/*                                                                                */
/*                               User Control Task                                */
/*                                                                                */
/*   This task is used to control your robot during the user control phase of     */
/*   a VEX Competition.                                                           */
/*                                                                                */
/*   BETWEEN THIS COMMENT AND THE USERCONTROL VOID ARE THE CONTROLLER FUNCTIONS.  */
